Package: HaploVar
Type: Package
Title: Defining Local Haplotype Variants for Use in Trait Association and Trait Prediction Analyses  
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person("Tessa", "MacNish", email = "tessa.macnish@uwa.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0008-8985-7348")), person("Hawlader", "Al-Mamun", role = "ctb"), person("Thomas", "Bergmann", role = "ctb"), person("Mitchell", "Bestry", role = "ctb"), person("Jacob", "Marsh", role = "ctb"), person("David", "Edwards", role = "ctb"))
Description: A local haplotyping tool for use in trait association and trait prediction analyses pipelines.
    HaploVar enables users take SNPs (in VCF format) and a LD matrix, calculate local haplotypes and format 
    the output to be compatible with a wide range of trait association and trait prediction tools.
